quote.p:
“Appreciating the spontaneous offers of assistance
                            to the Korean people which have been made by governments, specialized
                            agencies, and non-governmental organizations;

“Requests the Unified Command to provide the
                            Security Council with reports, as appropriate, on its relief
                            activities;

div.p:
Department please relay to London as USUN 3;
                        Paris USUN 3; Oslo USUN 3; New Delhi USUN 3;
                        Cairo USUN 3; Taipei USUN 2; Habana USUN 3; Quito USUN 1; Belgrade
                            USUN 2; Moscow USUN 2.
